{"tid":290830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友半年暈咗三次","createTime":"2017-06-20T05:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T08:11:42.000Z","uid":122182,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f67afc8b29ce0563c05d8cc480f71f6733003fb8","tid":290830,"uid":122182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:34:48.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲，無吸毒，無家族病史，<br />\n尋晚喺個焗焗地嘅地方傾偈，<br />\n講講下嘢佢突然呀⋯呀⋯咁就暈咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放平佢個人見佢呼吸微弱，<br />\n幫佢扇風之後醒返，但不停眨眼，想講又講唔到嘢咁，<br />\n我嘗試扶返起佢，結果又暈咗，<br />\n前後搞成20分鐘先清醒哂，<br />\n左右眼分別睇嘢無問題，雙眼一齊睇就見到重影，<br />\n過多10分鐘完全無事，淨係話好眼瞓。<br />\n問佢記唔記得發生咩事，只記得自己向後跌。<br />\n<br />\n佢之前睇過公立醫院，醫生話唔係發作緊果陣check唔到咩事，<br />\n而家大約3個月發作一次，<br />\n唔係每次都空氣差，<br />\n上網search有N種可能性導致佢暈。<br />\n<br />\n一般幾千蚊果D身體檢查會唔會check到咩事？"},{"pid":"985bc6adc54b2c80f78eeaf49262e9c015d42900","tid":290830,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"驗過血照過腦了？"},{"pid":"091e3662c3e04c9d0f0ce957bf88eab922460426","tid":290830,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"重影？有啲危險喎<br />\n去私家照下排除係腦瘤先？"},{"pid":"af1e54fc30c47f56568e427069b6b145b3a8a1f5","tid":290830,"uid":56139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"女仔？花名係T字頭？"},{"pid":"eafc9c8621b97a29dd9230df6d17c18bb27aecb3","tid":290830,"uid":122182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女仔？花名係T字頭？</blockquote><br />\n女仔，唔係T字頭。<br />\n你朋友有相同情況？"},{"pid":"72f9bf8c8eb0e00ff51ac0ecc3bcb93bc6bf937c","tid":290830,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"去私家啦，一係你去公立既話就揀瑪麗"},{"pid":"bc2dc711d63fd7ff7fd36e5c649baf74b46389f8","tid":290830,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"做個詳細啲檢查，四五千蚊。<br />\n<br />\n條命係你朋友自己既。<br />\n<br />\n希望你說服到佢唔好慳錢而搞到冇左條命。"},{"pid":"d7ca1c9c6250cd1f62c6e51a99a1c78fdf673151","tid":290830,"uid":122182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驗過血照過腦了？</blockquote><br />\n有驗血無照腦，<br />\n公立醫院話唔係緊急case無資源，<br />\n話如果下次休克咗咁入嚟先同佢照。<br />\n照腦貴，所以佢無去私家照呀。"},{"pid":"f3c078ec67a16326f01e7d94e4bfa88df65f77ab","tid":290830,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>驗過血照過腦了？</blockquote><br />\n有驗血無照腦，<br />\n公立醫院話唔係緊急case無資源，<br />\n話如果下次休克咗咁入嚟先同佢照。<br />\n照腦貴，所以佢無去私家照呀。</blockquote><br />\n痴線, 下次可能唔洗Check啦<br />\n暈既話可大可小, 都係check下穩陣"},{"pid":"0f7c3221e355f4ba273707a44b25d010328457a9","tid":290830,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"貧血"},{"pid":"7bd8783c7b03f97a68362b8374ede38277d560a0","tid":290830,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd7b7ae5c366720a83dddae5bb06f31a40e96319","tid":290830,"uid":87820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"仲唔撚照？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廿幾歲就想死？"},{"pid":"849e1ad73a27a58fea33a12641fc3287d8cf31c3","tid":290830,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"磁力共振五六千左右<br />\n你遲咗醫搞到傷殘或死亡，俾幾多錢你都冇用，你失去嘅一定多過你檢查同治療嘅錢<br />\n咁睇一萬幾千真係抵到爛"},{"pid":"c85b5ca4d9168997dd7dbf9eca2113db78663d77","tid":290830,"uid":122182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做個詳細啲檢查，四五千蚊。<br />\n<br />\n條命係你朋友自己既。<br />\n<br />\n希望你說服到佢唔好慳錢而搞到冇左條命。</blockquote><br />\n我都希望勸得郁，<br />\n佢個人好鬼畏疾忌醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f5451a33790255690feaf3ac1c138de43e3e40","tid":290830,"uid":122182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"